The food is good. If you are planning to get delivery from them forget it! They use two companies for delivery DoorDash and Postmate. I ordered via DoorDash a couple of months ago and after 2 hours never received anything. I could not even reach anyone from DoorDash as they didn't pick up the phone. Today, I tried Postmate (two stews.) Instead, I received 2 sandwitches. I called both Postmate and the restaurant. They were not able to tell me why this happened or even to correct the mistake. I suggested to Fiouna's (the person on the phone was the manager) that they should change delivery company, but they were not receptive to the suggestion. So this review reflects what happens if you try delivery. I have eaten in the restaurant before and the food is good (probably 4 stars).
